V , and later disputed the throne of England with her cousin  Stephen . In  1128  she married  Geoffrey , Count of Anjou. A medieval chronicler commented, ‘she was a good woman, but she had little bliss with him’. The name <i>Maud</i> became quite common in England in the 19th century, when its popularity was influenced in part by  Tennyson's  poem Maud, published in  1855 , but has not been much used since the early decades of the 20th century."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Maud Gerrard was born in 1380. She had at least 1 son with William Jenney. She died in 1400, at the age of 20."},"et":{"1380–1400":"1380–1400","1372–1466":"1372–1466","1398–1460":"1398–1460","1400":"1400","1466":"1466","1398":"1398","1460":"1460","1372":"1372","1380":"1380","Knowleshal, Suff, England":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1380–1400":"1380–1400","1372–1466":"1372–1466","1398–1460":"1398–1460","1400":"1400","1466":"1466","1398":"1398","1460":"1460","1372":"1372","1380":"1380","Knowleshal, Suff, England":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1380–1400":"1380–1400","1372–1466":"1372–1466","1398–1460":"1398–1460","1400":"1400","1466":"1466","1398":"1398","1460":"1460","1372":"1372","1380":"1380","Knowleshal, Suff, England":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Maud Gerrard est née en 1380. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec William Jenney. Elle est décédée en 1400, à l’âge de 20 ans."},"de":{"1380–1400":"1380–1400","1372–1466":"1372–1466","1398–1460":"1398–1460","1400":"1400","1466":"1466","1398":"1398","1460":"1460","1372":"1372","1380":"1380","Knowleshal, Suff, England":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Maud Gerrard wurde 1380 geboren. Sie hatte mit William Jenney mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb 1400 im Alter von 20 Jahren."},"ht":{"1380–1400":"1380–1400","1372–1466":"1372–1466","1398–1460":"1398–1460","1400":"1400","1466":"1466","1398":"1398","1460":"1460","1372":"1372","1380":"1380","Knowleshal, Suff, England":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1380–1400":"1380–1400","1